This set of schematics was taken from the OSU standard cell library for
GF180MCU (https://github.com/stineje/globalfoundries-pdk-libs-gf180mcu_osu_sc)
and adapted for use with the Open Circuit Design radiation-tolerant standard
cell library.

Still needs to be done:

Required editing:

All gates need to be corrected for W and L for the new layouts.
Fix the clocking on the flops.
Check all schematics for correctness.

Required new gates:

1. Majority-3	(gf180mcu_ocd_sc_rt7t3v3__maj3_2/4)
2. Antenna tie-down (gf180mcu_ocd_sc_rt7t3v3__ant)
3. Decap (gf180mcu_ocd_sc_rt7t3v3__decap_2/3/4/6/8/12)
4. Fill (gf180mcu_ocd_sc_rt7t3v3__fill_2/3/4/6/8/12) (even though the schematic
	is effectively empty)

Optional new gates:

1. Additional output strengths for all cells (preferably 1, 2, 4 for all
   major logic, and 1, 2, 4, 8, and 16 for the inverter, buffer, and clock
   inverter and buffer.
2. Additional OAI and AOI variations
3. Standard 3-input gates for NAND, NOR, AND, OR
4. Standard 4-input gates for NAND, NOR, AND, OR
5. OA and AO variations 
